        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «لاَ بَأْسَ أَنْ يَدْخُلَ اَلْمُحْرِمُ اَلْحَمَّامَ وَ لَكِنْ لاَ يَتَدَلَّكُ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2695 - Imam (as) said: \"There is no harm if a person in the state of ihram enters the bathhouse, but they should not scrub themselves.\""
        ]
